          <a href="/student/login" class="w-full rounded-xl border border-slate-300 bg-white px-3 py-2 text-center text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 hover:bg-slate-50">Login</a>
          <a href="https://techmindsacademy.org/application" class="w-full rounded-xl bg-blue-600 px-3 py-2 text-center text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-blue-700">Apply</a>
